Lani O'Grady https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lani_O%27Grady 0 Lani O'Grady (October 2, 1954 – September 25, 2001) was an American actress and talent agent. She is best-remembered for her role as Mary Bradford, the eldest sister from Eight Is Enough. Lani_O'Grady ( October_2_,_1954 – September_25_,_2001 ) was an_American_actress_and_talent_agent .
